data.description: Move in ready 1989 colonial with 2,250 sqft of living space on a private 2 acre lot!  Quiet country road setting just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and entertainment, this well maintained home features 4 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms with a fluid wrap-around layout perfect for modern living. Enjoy ample space on the spacious 2nd floor and entertain in style with the large finished walk-out basement.  Additional features include:  2 car garage and 200 amp electrical service.  Updates include:  New windows (2021), Newer roof (~2019), New Boiler (2021), New Water Heater (2021).  Sunrun solar panels ($173/mo) offset nearly 100% of the homes electric usage all year long allowing you to keep the house nice and cool in the summer without the outrageous costs. Don't miss the chance to make it yours! Call today to schedule a showing.
